{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} once you had I think you said a friend that was lodging with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Oh mr - Mr - Mr Wilkins - used to help ...
