Oh, some time. 'Til he - he - got - of course he had to come and lodge with use because he'd lost his brother you see and mother wouldn't - he couldn't - we would have him with us you see 'cos there was enough room - five bedrooms that was enough you see.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Did you ever have any lodgers in any of your other homes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 No, no, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 You mentioned that you had a woman who came in to do the washing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Oh yes. That's right. My mum did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Did you have anybody else coming in to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 
At times she did - when - when - before I was left school you see she used to have a woman come in you see - at the beginning of the week to do the rooms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 How many times a week would the woman come in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Only once - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11088960\charrsid9002493 On}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 
 the other days did your mother do cleaning - did she have a routine of set things on set days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Oh yes, she used to - you know - like I do - just make the beds and ho}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15282151\charrsid9002493 o}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 ver see. 'til I - 'til I left school then I - my sister and I used to help you see
. For the time - there's all - eight rooms you see, oh the two rooms was for the men that's right - yes, that's right. Six rooms really.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 And you also mentioned that in the photograph you had a blouse that you thought perhaps your sister had made?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 She did - yes. I've got that - I've got that photograph.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Did your mother make all your clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 She used to do a good bit - you see she has made some cloaks and bonnets. Used to make them nice too - and all our you know dresses - yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Were any of the clothes bought?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 
Oh yes. We had it for the boys you see and that used to be along where the - where the Euston tube station - where the Euston station is - not Euston station - down by Euston Road there on the corner used to be called Watts and something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Was that a stall or a shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 No, it was another shop - yes - very nice shop.
