\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 No, no. No, she used to go in the club - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 The boot club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Yes. And that was up at Dickses up in the {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}
Camden High Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Did she pay in regularly for the club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Oh yes, yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 How often was that?
