ause there's seven of us. Of course, my sister Grace, she went and lived with my grandmother you see, when us twins was born. It was too much 'cos we was fed on the bottle you see and we was long to you know - things we hadn't - she couldn't manage it you
 see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 For the club she didn't have to put in every single week though?
