Oh she wanted too yes. She used to go up there I suppose you know for the shoes or whatever it was up there 'cos there was a good many of us to go up there see, yes, we always
 - we always had our three pairs of shoes - we had one - used to have a Saturday pair of shoes from our day ones and also at Sunday times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Day ones, Saturday ones and Sunday ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Did you have different clothes on Saturdays from what you had in the week?
