Oh he would do - he used to keep up them - used to have to bring - we had like a pile you see to the office and he'd write all his tickets out you see I think 'cos they had to have a pass you see to go 
in these Government places and he had a lot - a lot of work to do there - and when the accounts come in you see there'd be a quarter - oh he had a lot to do - and it was beautifully done - oh he did write lovely.
