\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Probably get the coal up or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 What about helping with the children - did he help looking after them at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 No, no need to I don't think. Used to help ourselves I think. When there's a family I think they help one another don't you, really.

