No, 12 o'clock at night, and the poor little children Somers Town they used to have no socks or shoes on, terrible, and they used to pick all the stuff out, the rooten stuff out and eat it, they were so hungry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 And so what about the back bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 The back bedroom? That's my brothers \'85 in there. My eldest brother and the other two brothers was downstairs and of course Gil, \'85
 Gilbert was there in that bedroom, the cot you see, he was born in that room, and I was born upstairs and mother was born up there. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 What kind of a kitchen had you? Was it a big -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 No, it wasn't very big. It was out on its own like it was joined on like. It was nice, comfortable, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 \'85 what sort of stove?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Oh we had a kitchen stove, oh yes, had a kitchen stove and a sink and all in it, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 A range was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 A kitchen range, yes, a kitchen range, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 \'85
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 An Arlbert range I think they called it in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Did you have your meals there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 In there, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 I see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 And when mother had company they used to go down in the front room. We had to go upstairs and I used to see to them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 You used the front room then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Wel
l Dad used to be in the room for the office of course like he had all his books there because he had to do a lot of work you see, and then afterwards he used to clear it away and then put it on the cover and then put it back where the piano was, you see, 
like that, the back room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 You spent your evenings in the back room if you were in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Oh more or less often we went in there and had our tea we used to go downstairs you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Oh I see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 And Dad used to be always -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 ... men were -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Oh no the men were downstairs. When we had people come you know used to go down there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 In the basement?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 No not in the basement there, that's the other working men watching for the orders would come along.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Working me in the basement. Front room - father's office
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Yes up here, office and back room we had where we played the piano and that, yes. And that was their bedroom and that was our bedroom.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 I've got it straight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Oh you have. Funny thing I'd just find that wasn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 \'85
