\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 About sixteen I think there, dear. \'85. \'85.
