\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Yes it is, yes. I was going to throw it away. You can just see Duchers on it, \'85
 my great grandfather's, my name was Phillips. I see. And that's the blouse she made, the leg of mutton blouse you see, she made my blouse there I think or my sisters did
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 Nice aren't they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16122257 ED  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 It was in those days. I was upstairs making my bed. That's why I've got my sleeves all rolled up, doing my work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13721485 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1787301\charrsid9002493 \'85 photograph taken.
